          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1164.-step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and chop the <strong>waxy&nbsp;potatoes</strong> and <strong>carrots</strong> into large bite-sized pieces&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Add both the <strong>potatoes</strong> and <strong>carrots</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 15-20 min or until fork-tender</p>\r\n<p>Once tender, drain and leave to steam-dry (reserve the pan for step 6!)&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1164.-step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
